2002-1555 (La. 10/14/02)

Rufus GREEN, et al. v. BALMORAL ESTATES, L.L.C. No. 2002-CC-1555. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 14, 2002.

In re Balmoral Estates L.L.C.; — Defendant; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of East Feliciana, 20th Judicial District Court Div. A, No. 33,525; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, No. 2001 CW 2576.

Denied.

WEIMER, J., would grant the writ.
